{"tid":84931,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"GM Diet中，你問我答（秒回）","createTime":"2017-01-18T02:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T17:24:15.000Z","uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"555cd29b53646a1f8ee662522c896b4ae4eb2233","tid":84931,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:16:27.000Z","msg":"第一日：水果日<br />\n第二日：蔬菜日<br />\n第三日：水果蔬菜日<br />\n第四日：香蕉牛奶日<br />\n第五日：牛肉蔬菜日<br />\n第六日：牛肉蔬菜水果日<br />\n第七日：飯牛肉蔬菜水果日<br />\n<br />\n利申第四日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b881805eda7081b3e07b8e60b0aafaa3f2cb1f9","tid":84931,"uid":64648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:17:42.000Z","msg":"而家幾重，目標減到幾多？<br />\n會唔會做運動？"},{"pid":"6010b8827596bc9e8a3990196674d662838c6242","tid":84931,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"本身食肉獸忍到呢o的生活？"},{"pid":"d59348e4102ff1363b34d9d56efc58c2d1764901","tid":84931,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:22:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家幾重，目標減到幾多？<br />\n會唔會做運動？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家應該55樓下左右<br />\n本身無打算減肥，係打算排毒清腸胃<br />\n無做運動 簡左好耐唔知去邊間gym room好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee976c03b3f7ea2798bbe43fe7ee33eb866b0ef","tid":84931,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身食肉獸忍到呢o的生活？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 忍唔到 精神狀態好差 自問平時食得好清淡<br />\n我一食呢個餐單就瘋狂不停想食其他野 不過隔一陣唔去想就無事<br />\n但身體會話俾你知你飽左 同成日去廁所"},{"pid":"8ae2da102e0d8c554487eccc3d4be118b4fa5e62","tid":84931,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:25:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家幾重，目標減到幾多？<br />\n會唔會做運動？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n目標希望可以50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c252216e90635e0ab25f86130ca56497bd13d9b","tid":84931,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:31:39.000Z","msg":"秘密武器：蔬菜湯！這個湯非常重要！！當你在做下面的餐單的時候還是一樣餓到不行，你就可以做這個湯了，不管什麼時候只要你餓了你就可以喝這個湯，不管第一天還是最後一天，但是記住出了餐單上面說的，你只能喝這個湯哦！<br />\n<br />\n做法：材料其實是可以變通的，因為有人可能真的不喜歡下面的材料，我查過了是可以變通的但是要切忌不要加豆類。餐單上面介紹的是，番茄（番茄醬不可以哦），包心菜，洋蔥，芹菜，青椒，加水去煮就可以了。其實你可以自己加喜歡的蔬菜，我有加冬瓜，還有大蒜。味道還不錯，就是羅宋湯沒有肉跟番茄醬的味道。。。<br />\n<br />\n取自網絡<br />\n<br />\n呢個湯真心唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  飲完瘋狂去廁所"},{"pid":"d74bdd497bf50f40cc44aec3da588e80c369fcd4","tid":84931,"uid":5232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"淨係食呢啲呀？<br />\n其實平時少d肉少d飯多d菜都夠做 少食多餐 飯後水果咁"},{"pid":"96f55176227e9279af7d8b6db7b7356cb2e36638","tid":84931,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T04:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係食呢啲呀？<br />\n其實平時少d肉少d飯多d菜都夠做 少食多餐 飯後水果咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時我都係咁 但係上網話呢個餐單係可以排毒<br />\n<br />\n同埋飯後唔應該食水果 飯前食先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2beb8a695207e6416014f6d0b10b2676bc7222f5","tid":84931,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:06:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844050259c908f6e07a27ee84eb642621fd9f952","tid":84931,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T17:54:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淨係食呢啲呀？<br />\n其實平時少d肉少d飯多d菜都夠做 少食多餐 飯後水果咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時我都係咁 但係上網話呢個餐單係可以排毒<br />\n<br />\n同埋飯後唔應該食水果 飯前食先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食咁多牛點排"},{"pid":"c0828b0bd5df81bbd439ae56eea6ba3ebe44168a","tid":84931,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>淨係食呢啲呀？<br />\n其實平時少d肉少d飯多d菜都夠做 少食多餐 飯後水果咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時我都係咁 但係上網話呢個餐單係可以排毒<br />\n<br />\n同埋飯後唔應該食水果 飯前食先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食咁多牛點排</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你試頭幾日就會發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219bae7ea6672b3fb405a06c28984fc3df7fcc57","tid":84931,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:43:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b561d2bd7c2df898816a3d03d228983f20779be7","tid":84931,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:43:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0eb1069b343209d5f9c0e1c3473c44eb9299c622","tid":84931,"uid":139354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"最尾減唔減到？"},{"pid":"0982bf9ce4a34d2d6f33773f0397593320a846ca","tid":84931,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0eb1069b343209d5f9c0e1c3473c44eb9299c622","tid":84931,"uid":139354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"最尾減唔減到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T18:58:50.000Z","msg":"減到"},{"pid":"f5de1768d4288e4a48d10d29700effa3feaa9af3","tid":84931,"uid":139354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0982bf9ce4a34d2d6f33773f0397593320a846ca","tid":84931,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0eb1069b343209d5f9c0e1c3473c44eb9299c622","tid":84931,"uid":139354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"最尾減唔減到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T18:58:50.000Z","msg":"減到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:02:12.000Z","msg":"減咗幾多啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4903a13e82f8d7bac96570217cdedc18c7f0c9cd","tid":84931,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f